{"tid":2141633,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇師兄覺得少女終末旅行好有共嗚","createTime":"2020-08-06T00:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T03:43:31.000Z","uid":105678,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"240a0dbc50f8f5f8fac4c6407b89f2481898aab7","tid":2141633,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T00:05:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KLep8ub.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKLep8ub.jpg&h=6105faef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾年前追番睇過一次已經覺得好好睇，不過追住睇太有割裂感，上個禮拜又一次過重睇，好奇妙。<br />\n<br />\n中間有一集講音樂，落雨嗰part又夠原始夠純真，末日中自得其樂好有意境，冇比賽冇競爭，只有簡潔嘅音樂，對比手法用得好好，生命本應好似兩個o靚妹咁隨遇而安，多一日命仔就係上天賜福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開波牙千同優莉爭兵糧嗰個位又好真實，人喺冇選擇嘅時候食乜都會覺得好食，回憶翻以前喺法國外籍兵團受訓嗰陣，啲阿sir會特登畀食少啲糧餓下新兵，幾淡味嘅軍糧都覺得好好食。相信作者應該經歷過冇嘢食嘅日子先畫得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外首op都好好聽，可愛嘅少女喺殘酷嘅世界之中掙扎求存，完全係生命嘅寫照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920e3f3a4858a19127f42a009b314f802ad5d5f4","tid":2141633,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T00:11:02.000Z","msg":"樓主就快有得拍真人版"},{"pid":"8f30ea8e376dba6b1d3ed61113c811029510dea4","tid":2141633,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T00:20:45.000Z","msg":"神作"},{"pid":"791c1be287fa495c5ef2ac22763d589c574d7594","tid":2141633,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f30ea8e376dba6b1d3ed61113c811029510dea4","tid":2141633,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T00:20:45.000Z","msg":"神作"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T00:22:12.000Z","msg":"Mika有睇過嗎"},{"pid":"3cfd47c36effa49d713f85dce8c97dabffd51467","tid":2141633,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"791c1be287fa495c5ef2ac22763d589c574d7594","tid":2141633,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f30ea8e376db